\;x\in\Bbb R\;
\,e(x)\;
e'(x)=\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{nx^{n-1}}{n!}=\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac{x^{n-1}}{(n-1)!}=\sum_{n=0}^\infty\frac{x^n}{n!}=e(x)
\;e(x)=ke^x\;,\;k\in\Bbb R\;
\,e(0)=1\implies k=1\;
